Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.59,0:01:15.17,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}真希望能改變些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.17,0:01:18.89,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}既然想要個契機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.05,0:01:20.56,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}那就飛奔出去吧 Boooon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:24.73,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}回憶在騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:30.32,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我…好像認識你！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:34.44,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}不論是晴天雨天還是在下雪
